  | publisher =
  | date =
  | url =http://www.danielfaulkner.com/docs/SummaryofCaseFacts.pdf 
  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =  }}
</ref> He was at that time also the outgoing President of the [[Philadelphia Association of Black Journalists]].<ref>{{cite web
  | last =
  | first =
