  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =  }}</ref>

District Attorney [[Lynne Abraham]] has stated that the case was the "most open-and-shut murder case" she'd ever tried,<ref>>{{cite web
  | last =Gibson
  | first =Dave 
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors =
