  | accessdate =  }}
[]</ref> He accepted, and a recording of his speech was played at the commencement ceremony, being that he was not legally able to attend in person. The event was protested heavily by police officers from around the US. Among other schools whose graduates he has addressed are [[Antioch College]], [[UC Santa Cruz]], [[Kent State University]], [[Occidental College]].<ref>{{cite web
  | last =Reynolds 
  | first =Mark 
